		<article class="message-body js-selectToQuote">
			
				
			

			<div itemprop="text">
				
					<div class="bbWrapper">Personally, I really liked this chapter. Most of the time, I can't get through updates longer than 5k words, but Lords' writing is just so good that BCF is an exception to this. Every Wednesday now, I make time in the evenings to read the update, and every time I'm left wanting more. It's just such a good story, and Jozef is a really likable character for me. He's got his flaws, but that's what makes him great. He feels like a real individual and one that's taking strides to deal with his own flaws, and that's what elevates this story from great to exceptional.</div>
				
			</div>

			
	
	
		
	

<div class="js-selectToQuoteEnd">&nbsp;</div>
			
				
			
		</article>

		

		
	</div>

								

								
									
	

	

								

								
									
	
		
